<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="b1937_08_15_an_PattissonGilbert"><teiHeader><fileDesc> <titleStmt> <title>Von <persName key="WittgensteinLudwig" role="sender" full="yes">Ludwig Wittgenstein</persName> an <persName key="PattissonGilbert" role="recipient" full="yes">Gilbert Pattisson</persName>, [15. 8.? 1937]</title> <author>Wittgenstein, Ludwig</author> </titleStmt> <publicationStmt> <p>Ludwig Wittgenstein: Gesamtbriefwechsel, 2. Auflage</p> </publicationStmt> <sourceDesc default="false"> <p>Original an der Trinity College Library; Kopie im BA.</p> </sourceDesc> </fileDesc><profileDesc> <creation>Brief geschrieben am 1937_08_15.</creation> </profileDesc><encodingDesc><p>TEI P5</p></encodingDesc><revisionDesc><list type="simple"><item>2007/06: Conversion from Folio Flat File to XML</item><item>2018/12: Added to Innsbruck Correspondence Edition</item></list></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div type="transcript" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"> <p rend="indent">Wishing</p> <p rend="indent">My</p> <p rend="indent">FRIEND</p> <p rend="indent">A Happy</p> <p rend="indent">BIRTHDAY</p> <p rend="indent">Birthday greetings</p> <p rend="indent">love sincere</p> <p rend="indent">Happy days be yours my dear,</p> <p rend="indent">From your loyal friend and true,</p> <p rend="indent">Speeds this greetings</p> <p rend="indent">card to you.</p> <p rend="indent">GOOD</p> <p rend="indent">LUCK</p> <p>G. R. Pattisson Esq</p> <p>42 Argyll Rd.</p> <p>Kensington</p> <p>London W.8.</p> <p rend="right">[Poststempel: EXETER, 15 ? 1937]</p> <p rend="indent">I shall be at the pallace to-morrow, Friday, 6 p.m.. I hope you wont be busybodying in your office on Saturday.</p> <p rend="indent">bl...</p> <p rend="right">Ludwig</p> <p rend="indent">Remember, even Bismarck could be replaced.</p> <p rend="indent">Keep this card till your [100th ?] birthday.</p> </div></body></text></TEI>